edu.vt.middleware.ldap.handler
Class CompareAuthorizationHandler

java.lang.Object
  edu.vt.middleware.ldap.handler.CompareAuthorizationHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
AuthorizationHandler
public class CompareAuthorizationHandler
extends Object
implements AuthorizationHandler

CompareAuthorizationHandler performs a compare operation with a custom filter. The DN of the authenticated user is automatically provided as the {0} variable in the search filter arguments.

process

public void process(AuthenticationCriteria ac,
                    LdapContext ctx)
             throws NamingException
Process an authorization after an ldap authentication. The supplied LdapContext should not be closed in this method. Implementations should throw AuthenticationExceptione to indicate an authorization failure.

Specified by:
